1381
01:33:50,832 --> 01:33:52,467
dan di sini.

1382
01:33:52,500 --> 01:33:54,669
Dan juga di sana.

1383
01:34:02,844 --> 01:34:06,782
Saya mungkin dah menulis
satu buku lagi.

1384
01:34:15,524 --> 01:34:16,859
Hannah.

1385
01:34:20,262 --> 01:34:22,231
Awak... Awak nyata.

1386
01:34:22,264 --> 01:34:23,365
Awak dah pulang.

